verse = \lyricmode {
  May prin -- ces, moved by awe and won -- der,
then trav -- el miles on miles,
that they may him the trib -- ute ren -- der
of Tar -- shish and the isles.
May Shee -- ba with its gifts a -- dore him,
and Se -- ba trea -- sures bring.
May rul -- ers all fall down be -- fore him
and serve him as their king.
}
